    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for discerning drivers is this BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS rebuild to ensure peak performance and structural integrity. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise engagement, transferring power through the variable M differential lock for optimal traction. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, preserving the iconic handling characteristics of this platform. While it exhibits minor aesthetic wear commensurate with its age, the mechanical systems are thoroughly sorted, delivering a visceral and analog driving experience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
